<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Nemshs Ooan could use a helping hand with a necessary evil.
Greetings, honored guessst. Could you perchance lend an old Ondo a hand with a troublesome hunt?
Dagons pose a threat to the young and infirm, for they disguise themselves as rocks and ambush their prey to feed. They must be culled for the good of all, but I alone cannot see this done.
Therefore I would ask you to help me in ssslaying the meddlesome pests. A trio should sssuffice. Come and see me when you have finished.
You need not slay ten ssscore or some other ungodly amount, my friend. Three dagons alone would be a tremendous help.
Say no more, honored guest. The dagons are dead. I can smell their blood on you.

Like the Ondo, they too seek to take shhhelter in the ancient ruins. It is a regrettable state of affairs that we must ever ssstrive to keep their numbers in check, else they drive us out of hearth and home.
It will only be more difficult to do so in the absence of water...but such is our life now. There is naught to be gained from pining for what was lossst...
